post.body: Holy crap! Better get coffee tomorrow! I'm still studying! Boo! But time for sleep!
It's about time!!
That's what I was just watching on ch 7's news!! And didn't it seem like secret service was lagging in getting to him?
Lack of water, eliminated diet coke & dry weather...but whatever. Now I'm sick from all the coughers at my office!
How did you know?
I had the same thing last week! Remember?
I'm not sure. I have to check w/my dad. I'm so pissed!
I thought they would have all upgraded YEARS ago. I mean with all their revenue.
eek. I hope that guy wasn't a doctor! He looked more like a hipster.
Ok, cool. I'm a wine novice. Thanks!
I feel naked if I don't have it on!
My dad was like that for a long time. But now that he's a grandpa, he always wears his seat belt!
Late reply. They didn't stop me! But I would have passed!
Late reply! New York & Co, Gap, Bath & Body (they had 30%). Nothing too exciting.
Just the way the baby Jesus intended it to be...
Night!
Ever feel bad about the majority of the world hating one person's guts?
Hearing strange sounds outside. Realized it was rain.
Half of me is sad it's Sunday & the other half is ok with it. I just want finals to be over!
I guess its a good thing I didn't see it b/c I would have gone off on the ass hole & who knows, they probably would have shot me.
Some STUPID FUCK HIT MY CAR AT THE GHETTO ASS LAUNDROMAT. Im not even here for 10 minutes and this happens.
Heading out to do laundry!
Waiting for Mediterranean pizza cooking up in the oven & study for Marketing
OMG! This dude here at Starbucks has a pager on his belt! Have not seen one in years!
Finished meeting with my group. One girl complains of doing a lot of work but is such a control freak & wants to do everything.
It's official, I'm sick! Freaking coughers at new job! Only 2 weeks in & they got me sick. Last time I was sick, June 2007.
Watching True Life on MTV...people in prison.
So does wine have to go in the fridge once you open it?
Old Navy was severely picked over but I managed to pick up a few shirts that I desperately needed!
About to enter 2nd Old Navy of the day. Wish me luck!
This girl here at Sbux passes me on my left where there's about 3" of space instead of going the other way where there's 3' of space. Lame.
Got a 2009 little desk calendar at the Hello Kitty store & a pen. Will try to head to Old Navy.
South Coast = Fail
So sad that I had to leave the Fresh store. I guess my one bottle of $26 shampoo wasn't worth their time.
In the parking lot not 2 seconds & Im already leaning on my horn. Happy Holidays!
South Coast Plaza. I have met my match - this place is insane. And Im not even in the parking lot yet!
Less than $20 to fill up my Corolla! Yay!
Just waking up...still tired. Must head out to South Coast. Not too worried about it. Parking has never been a problem there.
My ears go back & forth from being plugged to popping. It's the remaining effects of being sick earlier this week. It's so annoying!
So back in the day, Toys r Us was the greatest place ever. And now, it's all ghetto!
